 to outrun them or whatever they return to the hut.  Normally you will then find them on top of the hut.  The tunics they drop sell to the merchants for about 60pp each so good loot.<br>
<br>
Orsmo Xlorr<br>
44level Wizard<br>
Prexus <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unarach.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Narach</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/23/01 1:04:16 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> RE: Learning to Kite spot</span><hr size=1> Once you hit level 29, and want to start kiting, a very simply way to practice is go back to the mind teen zones, like nRo, sRo etc. Then just load up your lower DDs, and practise kiting them, this takes away the risk of dying, and you can learn when not to stop and cast etc from the message:<br>
<br>
a dune tarantula tries to hit YOU but misses!<br>
a dune tarantula tries to hit YOU but misses!<br>
<br>
This is how im currently learning how to quad kite, only problem is that you wont know about likely resistances, how hard the mobs hit etc ... but at least you will have had practise before hand.<br>
<br>
Narach<br>
37th Wizard of the Red Wolf Clan<br>
Zeb server <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufieht.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fieht</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/27/01 5:53:52 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RE: Learning to Kite spot</span><hr size=1> A good place to practice Quadding is in LOIO at the broken tower with four Gobs in it dtraight out from the windmill.  They will all be blue and die very quickly.  At 29 I could kill them with 2 bubs of mana left...even with resists.  That is why it is a good place...there are enough resists to keep you on your feet but not enough risk to get you killed (I only died once when I snared myself...hehe...never try to talk and quad)<br>
<br>
-Nigh <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvodreaux.showPublicProfile?language=EN>vodreaux</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/30/01 8:13:25 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Learning to Kite spot - I say Lions in Ek</span><hr size=1> Learning to Quad-Kite lions in Ek.  Even after 29 you don't get experience, you do get pelts.<br>
<br>
I do it all the time! so I can get as many HQ Cat pelts for Tailoring practice Quivers. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showMessage?topicID=167.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showMessage?topicID=140.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=153.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.threadControl?topicID=153.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=153.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=153.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Ma